      <title>鲍威尔称期待与特朗普政府保持良好关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/powell-says-he-expects-good-relations-with-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，他有信心与新一届政府，包括财政部长提名人斯科特·贝森特建立类似的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/powell-says-he-expects-good-relations-with-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 19:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友批评联邦工作人员在家办公延期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-allies-blast-work-from-home-extension-for-federal-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的盟友批评了一项将部分联邦工作人员的混合工作选择延长至 2029 年的协议，称社会保障局与其工会之间的协议破坏了重返办公室的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-allies-blast-work-from-home-extension-for-federal-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚总统称其财政部长预计将辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/colombian-president-says-finance-chief-bonilla-expected-to-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚财政部长里卡多·博尼利亚 (Ricardo Bonilla) 预计将在政府试图推动国会提高税收的关键阶段辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/colombian-president-says-finance-chief-bonilla-expected-to-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普更换白宫法律顾问人选，任命戴维·沃灵顿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-swaps-white-house-counsel-pick-tapping-david-warrington</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将任命戴维·沃灵顿 (David Warrington) 为白宫法律顾问，代替他的竞选律师担任之前宣布的总统首席内部律师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-swaps-white-house-counsel-pick-tapping-david-warrington</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皮特·赫格塞斯 (Pete Hegseth) 防守中锋机会越来越少，现在轮到恩斯特了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hegseth-s-narrowing-chances-for-defense-post-now-turn-on-ernst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的国防部长候选人皮特·赫格塞斯很可能将在周三下午与退伍军人共和党参议员乔尼·恩斯特会面时，面临国会山迄今为止最严厉的质询。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hegseth-s-narrowing-chances-for-defense-post-now-turn-on-ernst</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大油砂之乡追逐 710 亿美元数据中心机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/home-of-canada-s-oil-sands-chases-71-billion-data-center-opportunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大阿尔伯塔省拥有世界第三大原油储量，该省正努力成为人工智能数据中心的枢纽，并有潜力吸引 1000 亿加元（710 亿美元）的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/home-of-canada-s-oil-sands-chases-71-billion-data-center-opportunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:16:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲必须重新聚焦资本市场联盟努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/europe-must-refocus-capital-markets-union-efforts-lagarde-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德在《经济学人》的一篇专栏文章中表示，欧盟需要加大力度统一其分散的金融基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/europe-must-refocus-capital-markets-union-efforts-lagarde-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择前美国证券交易委员会委员阿特金斯接替詹斯勒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-names-paul-atkins-as-sec-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保罗·阿特金斯（Paul Atkins）是一位资深金融监管者，也是华盛顿保守派金融圈的固定人物，他是候任总统唐纳德·特朗普选择的人选，将领导并可能改革美国证券交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-names-paul-atkins-as-sec-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命万斯助手盖尔·斯莱特为司法部反垄断高级官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-vance-aide-gail-slater-as-top-doj-antitrust-cop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普已选定盖尔·斯莱特 (Gail Slater) 担任司法部反垄断执法主管，斯莱特是当选副总统 JD 万斯的经济政策顾问，毕业于牛津大学。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-vance-aide-gail-slater-as-top-doj-antitrust-cop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
